{"type": "article", "id": 32989, "title": "GAP股票开始上涨，以及，LV 给手机壳提供了新思路 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-10-08T02:36:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 33651, "name": "圣诞限定美妆"}, {"id": 33652, "name": "iPhone 手机壳"}, {"id": 1678, "name": "植村秀"}, {"id": 1746, "name": "Snapchat"}, {"id": 2326, "name": "Gap"}, {"id": 3350, "name": "Louis Vuitton"}, {"id": 9470, "name": "Vans"}, {"id": 10726, "name": "Dior Homme"}, {"id": 14370, "name": "reebok"}, {"id": 25221, "name": "VF"}, {"id": 33653, "name": "Tiffany&Co."}, {"id": 11092, "name": "村上隆"}, {"id": 17322, "name": "Gigi Hadid"}, {"id": 24017, "name": "Robert Pattinson"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161008081346f2Zv94NjIkPUD1X8.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/gap-september-stock-comp-fishkill-fire-10658262/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Gap 股票大涨</b></a> | Gap 的股价在上周五的交易中涨了 15.3%，至 26.26 美元每股。该公司表示，它的可比销售额下降了 3%。美国富国银行（WELLS FARGO）的分析师指出，尽管 Gap 的业绩好于预期，面对年底的关键假期，仍然有很多不确定性因素。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-10-05/north-face-owner-will-elevate-its-operating-chief-to-ceo-role\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>VF 集团要换新的 CEO</b></a> | VF 集团是全球最大的服装制造商之一，旗下包括 The North Face 等多个品牌。现年 57 岁的 Rendle 将接替 Eric Wiseman 的工作，成为 VF 集团新的 CEO。他之前也是 The North Face 的 CEO。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2016/10/03/grana-10-million-series-a/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Grana 获 1000 万美元 A 轮投资</b></a> | Grana 是一家成立于香港的时尚电商，它最近宣布它获得了来自阿里巴巴领投的 1000 万美元投资。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>奢侈品电商网站 Moda Operandi 与 Tiffany&amp;Co. 合作，推出了 <a href=\"http://popbee.com/wedding/moda-operandi-wedding-dresses-fall/#\" rel=\"nofollow\">11 套 Exclusive 限量婚纱系列</a>。每一套都配上了特定的 Tiffany&amp;Co. 钻石珠宝。这 11 款时尚的婚纱接受 Moda Operandi 网上订购，价格由 3995 至 19920 美元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008081806onGXgLVpij5AhqbD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610080818065xCE3zjIV8tXyvHm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008081807U28nRsFktoJKiD37.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008081807WSuOT2x9GNFCmMvd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008081807ftYTZrO4RyBMcVLD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610080818078SyMA0W2Og9G1hoX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008081823l3dXZAJLUr8PkWyQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008081823CyO17jWiBrNVkT96.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008081950ZG7TPzlNRfJFMuVj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610080820222O4GTpUvISPw0Xye.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Robert Pattinson 演绎 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/robert-pattinson-dior-homme\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dior Homme 2016 </a>秋冬宣传大片。这组宣传照由 Karl Lagerfeld 亲自掌镜。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008082040tjT0D5OUzHu93xWb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610080820483KmwzVYaTiDl2A8h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008082059kyAna3UmKXiIfuzo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://popbee.com/accessories/shoes/vans-x-toy-story/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vans 与《玩具总动员》推出了联名系列</a>。鞋款以 Vans 最经典的 Old Skool、Era 与 Sk8-Hi 为基础，加入了《玩具总动员》中的人物元素。另外，鞋底上的仿墨水笔涂上的 ANDY 字样也是一处小惊喜。据官方消息称，该系列鞋款作为假日系列，将在今年 12 月推出。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008082104xUQTp7ProJgKqeOR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665957\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008082120RCm5D0acjGesiT9b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008082120CUcnd2BwDtE96p8P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008082120i98AHsjqwu07COdG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008082131tUJecdqxSM2BRkFm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008082131qhAg0dF8WwbpTVvS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008082139d92jCTQbZxGrHcfD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">时隔三年，<a href=\"http://popbee.com/beauty/make-up/shu-uemura-and-artist-takashi-murakami-team-up-for-the-best-holiday-beauty-gift/\" rel=\"nofollow\">植村秀再度与村上隆合作</a>，推出 2016 圣诞限定美妆。该系列加入了村上隆著名的微笑小花图案，包含卸妆油、眼线笔、唇膏等多款美妆产品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008082150X8P7xnDHEIthwyFZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008082201K1h7rade0FJSU5q8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008082212Ak5xC9VhtviU4cdR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Louis Vuitton 在 2017 春夏女装系列发布会上带来了一系列引人注目的<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/louis-vuitton-iphone-cases\" rel=\"nofollow\"> iPhone Case </a>新作。这个系列的手机壳采用了以当红手袋 Petite Maille 为原型的方正外型，搭配经典的 Monogram 印花皮革和鳄鱼皮，以金属细节和边框为点缀，极尽奢华。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008082225E0GPT6jSMCsiQwl8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008082225SPDbJniUeuIFOj5T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610080822257eCoxrBjLpyfJziq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008082226Mm70jkzJgnG4WlH8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008082226C2c01N4dZORMTlKp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008082239DjF3HhGPRqVuUaWT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008082239WAYjOkL7noXc6a9K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/gigi-hadid-reebok\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gigi Hadid 成为 Reebok 最新企划 PerfectNever 的形象大使</a>。在该系列的广告宣传片中，Gigi 一改往日的性感形象，以硬朗的拳击风格出境。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">&nbsp;<figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008082250Bz1jRhq7Kbi6OQNM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008082250SVedrpFEAXG06UTO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008082250qFlw4dIkzupKc2vo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008082250Jfg4aijHv8WBspT3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008082300gqetQzI0yYXObfPN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008082300OCkdE2tL0Jm4ohWN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}